<h2>Reset your password</h2>

<p>We received a request to reset the password for your <strong><%= @app_name %></strong> account.</p>

<a href="<%= @reset_url %>" class="btn">Reset Password</a>

<hr class="divider">

<p class="muted">
  This link expires in <strong>1 hour</strong>. After that, you'll need to request a new one.
</p>

<p class="muted">
  If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this URL:<br>
  <a href="<%= @reset_url %>" style="color: #666; word-break: break-all;"><%= @reset_url %></a>
</p>

<p class="muted">If you didn't request a password reset, no action is needed — your password is still safe.</p>
